{"tid":99941,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人聽錄音試過出現以下情況","createTime":"2017-01-29T15:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T10:50:50.000Z","uid":27601,"like":12,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26a49598696286d9e62c7a5e29c12a402b0a1208","tid":99941,"uid":27601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:03:58.000Z","msg":"我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呀哥：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老豆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事源：老豆想叫呀哥幫book機票<br />\n我同老豆係屋企<br />\n老豆：仔，幫我訂機票<br />\n我：ok<br />\n我：來回機票要2XXX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆：我再問問你哥搵其他<br />\n<br />\n我哥係hall，以下為wtsapp對話<br />\n老豆：仔，幫我訂機票<br />\n哥：ok<br />\n幾分鐘後<br />\n哥：（錄音）搵到了，來回3XXX<br />\n<br />\n老豆聽電話咁聽段錄音：咪住咪住咪住，你細路搵到2XXX喎！<br />\n老豆：喂？<br />\n老豆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哥：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9e2cb5cea8374fa6c82837f961003fbf8ee505","tid":99941,"uid":27601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4c768f37ae0379146958711f0d52c5e90d3e9f","tid":99941,"uid":27601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bca87981c1c762785d45bfc722808f0ed0a5f05","tid":99941,"uid":57864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/87m53gfj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F87m53gfj&h=42f21fa3&s={SIZE}\" /